  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0b8e\u0bb2 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bc0\u0baa\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bc1 - \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb5\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Firing on Kimbula Pradeep - Incident at Puduchettitheru in broad daylight",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo \u2013 Kimbula Pradeep, who is said to be linked to underworld activities, was injured in a broad daylight shooting at Puduchetti Street under the Coastal Police Division.",
        "Police Spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Nihal Talduwa said that the shooting was carried out at Hinny Appuhami Junction by unidentified people who came on a motorcycle around 12 noon today.",
        "The man was traveling on a motorcycle with his wife when the men on another motorcycle opened fire with a pistol and fled. Police said that the injured person has been admitted to the National Hospital.",
        "A hospital spokesperson said that a gunshot wound was observed in his abdomen.",
        "While the coastal police have started investigations, the police have recovered two empty cartridges used for pistols from the spot.",
        "The reason for the shooting and the suspects were not immediately known, but the police have carried out further investigations."
      ],
